v1.0.0 (30 Mar 2015)
  The 'db' connection object is now mandatory.
  Removed the 'mongodb' dependency.

v0.4.0 (23 Mar 2015)
  The default projection now returns the '_id' field.

v0.3.0 (03 Feb 2015)
  "drop()" now can receive an array of collections or an object whose keys are
    collection names.

v0.2.0 (31 Jan 2015)
  Added "drop()" function and added collection caching.

v0.1.0 (26 Jan 2015)
  First release.